Package: kassepcea
Title: Cost-Effectiveness of the KASSEP Maternal Mortality Surveillance System
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Baba Maiyaki", "Musa", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Decision-analytic model, deterministic and probabilistic sensitivity
    analyses, and publication figures for the cost-effectiveness analysis of a
    community-based sample registration system with verbal and social autopsy in
    Kano State, Nigeria.
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: ggplot2, scales, jsonlite
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
